= Install on debian/ubuntu

noise requires the numm library (http://numm.org/numm/) and all
associated dependencies:

$ wget http://numm.org/numm/releases/python-numm_0.1-1_all.deb
# dpkg -i python-numm_0.1-1_all.deb

the three noisegames will then run as standard python scripts:

$ git clone git://numm.org/noise
$ cd noise
$ python noise0.py
$ python noise1.py
$ python noise2.py

